column3:
“Very tasty bud, keeps you up with no crash. Very nice head 

#420sweepstakes”
“Really good uplifting high... Only thing I didn't like is how it sheds... Besides that, clean almost piney scent and productivity doesn't drop during work hours”
“Plenty pizzazz here. Very cerebral, spacey, reeling head high. Not much to report re: body. Cool visual/perceptual effects. A Sativa lover's dream.”
“Just like the description, good to share with your buds. This had me pretty talkative and interested in conversing. Made me feel a little drunk when I stood up. Got me blazed.”
“This is some quality loud. The fruity scent is almost immediately noticeable and the high is so funny. That's some dank shit”
“tried this strain a couple of months ago. hands down the best tasting bud I have ever had, this is my favorite strain that I have tried before”
“Keeps me going throughout the day with a big smile ;) no crash. Melts my pain and anxiety away!! It’s a must strain every other month for me.”
“Very strong head high. Very piney on the exhale. Very dense and full of trichomes.”
